            </p>

            <p>
                Which voter(s) <em>need</em> to keep voting “yes” in order for the motion to pass?
            </p>

            <p>
                <m>P_{3}, P_{4}</m> could change their minds without changing the outcome. <m>P_{1}</m> and <m>P_{2}</m> will change the outcome if they change their minds.
            </p>

            <p>
            </p>
